{"tid":1864353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府頒緊急令強制市民洗手","createTime":"2020-02-05T14:24:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T14:31:40.000Z","uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3612df9edb6e15cfc537c76a8ffcffe613ed75e9","tid":1864353,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T14:24:12.000Z","msg":"連登政府現頒布緊急令<br />\n如有市民回家後拒絕洗手<br />\n可報警求助<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你屋企有冇老人家仲係死都唔肯洗手?<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1861702\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1861702</a><br />\n<br />\n以上絕對唔係單一個案<br />\n再睇下資料<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3958723/org/530c8a1b2acf55c68bff6788fe3baf45.png/pNRdJvK5zCUFKDB7CljTnrOl2OXNIH67wQX2sMEF9rA?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3958723%2Forg%2F530c8a1b2acf55c68bff6788fe3baf45.png%2FpNRdJvK5zCUFKDB7CljTnrOl2OXNIH67wQX2sMEF9rA%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=8da356f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n45歲以上人士佔七成六<br />\n根據2019年年中統計<br />\n45歲以上人士佔香港人口一半<br />\n但係中招率高過45歲以下人士兩成半<br />\n<br />\n如果只計本港人士<br />\n依然有七成<br />\n由十六宗起嘅本地感染個案睇<br />\n6宗入面有4宗係高齡人士<br />\n由於其中有父傳母女個案<br />\n所以歸納為4宗<br />\n4宗入面有3個係高齡人士<br />\n依然高達七成半<br />\n<br />\n點解會有咁嘅現象？<br />\n因為老一輩人衛生意識差<br />\n依然有「大菌食細菌」「周圍都係菌啦」呢D落後思想<br />\n大部份高齡人士都冇洗手習慣<br />\n<br />\n呼籲洗手有乜撚用<br />\n屋企只要有一個人唔洗手<br />\n九成冚家剷<br />\n<br />\n口罩就識搶<br />\n最重要嘅洗手就唔撚做<br />\n唔用緊急法強制市民洗手<br />\n香港好快變疫埠<br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲記得睇實屋企高齡人士<br />\n硬功唔得就軟功<br />\n唔洗手唔俾入屋企唔聽就動之以情<br />\n一講洗手保全家平安<br />\n九成都會自動波<br />\n如果都係勸唔掂就報警當家庭糾紛啦<br />\n總之要洗手洗手洗手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d73d8305b6c9f9e66faa9314b49846de6978cf1a","tid":1864353,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T14:26:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06915bcaf911b2ac629c6d795e599e309a4721a9","tid":1864353,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T14:30:33.000Z","msg":"香港政府冇撚用<br />\n就由連登政府做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e9c2442f36c7b89325afd371302773fee2ef2ab","tid":1864353,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T14:31:40.000Z","msg":"仲係度笑D柒頭搶廁紙有乜用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n殺到埋身喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}